---
title: Southwest Beef Nacho Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: This family-style nacho bar will delight the whole table! You’ll set out a spread of taco-style ground beef and tender roasted fajita-style veggies plus toppers galore: homemade queso, crispy baked homemade tortillas chips, tomato, lime wedges, and sour cream, then let everyone build their own perfect nachos! Order lettuce for nacho lettuce cups or add guacamole to the bar!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66b1500b78d91450badf816f-1715295d.jpeg
